snippet.title: How to find the AREA OF A RECTANGLE: THE EASY WAY!
snippet.description: Go to http://mathmotor.com/e-tutoring/ for LIVE online tutoring! Check out this colorful and fun video and learn how to find the area of a Rectangle!  You need to know the length and the width of a rectangle to find the area.  Enjoy learning how to find the area of a rectangle with Youtube's Math Motor Channel!
